1. Modify megastore/src/presentation.md to change the content
2. Run make in this directory (megastore/ directory)
3. Make should create build/presentation-output.html in the build directory
4. Open build/presentation-output.html in your favorite browser.
5. See http://io-2012-slides.googlecode.com/git/template.html to know the
keyboard shortcuts and all the features supported.
6. This fork also supports another shortcut "z" which zooms in or out of the
slides to fit 90% of the available window.

